<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<!-- Standard Meta -->
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">

	<!-- Site Properities -->
	<title><%= title %></title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/libs/semantic/semantic.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/about.css">
</head>
<body>
	<!-- Page Contents -->
	<div class="pusher">
		<% include common/nav %>

		<div class="ui vertical inverted stripe segment title">
			<div class="ui middle aligned stackable grid container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="column">
						<h1><%= header %></h1>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="ui vertical stripe segment">
			<div class="ui middle aligned stackable grid container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="ten wide column">
						<p><b>
							My name is Tom Fischer, and I am from Teeswater Ontario. I am studying Software Engineering at Western University, and I completed my third year in the spring of 2015. Currently, I am working as a Software Developer intern at IBM in Markham, Ontario.
						</b></p>
						<p>
							I have designed and developed various applications and websites over the years. Most of my projects are written using NodeJS, Java, C#, or C++. Along with these skills, I also have experience with SQL and NoSQL databases.
						</p>
						<p>
							Besides programming, I enjoy playing sports, snowboarding, and snowmobiling. I have played hockey and baseball for most of my life, and I continue to play today. I also play recreational badminton and innertube water polo at Western University.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="six wide column">
						<img src="/images/tom-alt-min.JPG" class="ui rounded image">
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="ui vertical inverted stripe segment">
			<div class="ui middle aligned center aligned stackable grid container">
				<div class="three column row">
					<div class="column">
						<h1>
							<i class="huge github icon"></i><br>
							<a href="https://github.com/tgfischer" class="ui huge inverted right labeled icon button" target="_blank">
								GitHub Profile <i class="right arrow icon"></i>
							</a>
						</h1>
					</div>
					<div class="column">
						<h1>
							<i class="huge file text icon"></i><br>
							<a class="ui huge inverted green right labeled icon button" target="_blank">
								Download Resume <i class="download icon"></i>
							</a>
						</h1>
					</div>
					<div class="column">
						<h1>
							<i class="huge stack overflow icon"></i><br>
							<a href="http://stackoverflow.com/users/2455765/tfischer" class="ui huge inverted orange right labeled icon button" target="_blank">
								Stack Overflow Profile <i class="right arrow icon"></i>
							</a>
						</h1>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<% include common/footer %>
	</div>

	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/libs/semantic/semantic.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>

</body>

</html>
